# Podcast Generation System

You are working on an AI-powered podcast generation system that creates complete podcast episodes (audio + video + show notes) from a topic prompt.

## Key Documentation
- Full workflow: See `docs/WORKFLOW.md`
- Architecture: See `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`
- API integrations: See `docs/API_INTEGRATIONS.md`

## Core Technologies
- **LLM**: Google Gemini 3 (content analysis, script writing, show notes)
- **TTS**: Google Cloud Text-to-Speech (natural voice synthesis with Neural2 voices)
- **Video**: Google Veo + Remotion (visual generation)
- **Data Source**: YouTube Data API (English podcasts only)

## System Modules (11 steps)
1. Topic Input & Discovery (YouTube API)
2. Reference Selection
3. Transcription Retrieval
4. Content Analysis (Gemini)
5. Outline Generation (Gemini + human)
6. Script Writing (Gemini 3)
7. Fact-Checking (optional)
8. Text-to-Speech (Google Cloud TTS)
9. Video Generation (Veo + Remotion)
10. Show Notes (Gemini)
11. Final Assembly

## Important Constraints
- YouTube-only sources
- English language only
- Must produce: audio file, video file, show notes with timestamps
